SSRF :
Is a vuln which arries when application fetches resources from other server without validating users input in URL/Request.

####### Where to check ########
API Endpoints Accepting URLs or HTTP Requests
Any feild taking any web adress or IP Address
Whereever we see URL/IP in request header.

########## Mitigations ############
Block Localhost and Internal IPs
Whitelist Allowed Hosts
Block Outbound Requests
Limit Internal Access
Monitor and Log Requests
